9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 17=

11
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:45,479
Pei Du!

12
00:00:45,479 --> 00:00:46,000
Watch out!

13
00:00:50,399 --> 00:00:51,359
Stop her!

14
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:52,719
Pei Du!

15
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,159
Let go of me!

16
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:02,479
Let go of me!

17
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:04,959
Let go!

18
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,959
Yue Qin, let him go!

19
00:01:11,879 --> 00:01:12,680
Pei Du!

20
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,400
Your...

21
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,480
Your Highness,

22
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:26,400
don't cry.

23
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:29,159
Please... Please...

24
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:33,959
tell His Highness I'm sorry.

25
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,760
Pei Du!

26
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:52,400
Yue Qin, have you lost your mind?

27
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:53,799
I told you

28
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:55,560
the Emperor was using you!

29
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:57,319
Why won't you listen?

30
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,239
Why?

31
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,200
Mei Lin, let me explain.

32
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,719
The Emperor promised me

33
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,799
that if he died,

34
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,760
he'd let us go back to Zhao together.

35
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:09,319
We'd never have to live in fear again.

36
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,800
Even now,

37
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:13,360
you still refuse to wake up.

38
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,719
You didn't just help the tyrant
cover it up

39
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,240
and ruin my revenge plan.

40
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,719
You even killed Mr. Pei!

41
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:20,560
How come

42
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,120
you've become like this?

43
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,560
I just want you now.

44
00:02:26,319 --> 00:02:28,360
Mei Lin, I'll take you home.

45
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,199
Let go of me!

46
00:02:50,740 --> 00:02:54,860
(Yue Qin, Shadow Bureau)

47
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,120
Your Highness, tell me,

48
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,319
what does the writing mean?

49
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,439
Mei Lin...

50
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:04,039
Did Yue Qin take her from here?

51
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,919
I was one step too late.

52
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,280
I'll go save her.

53
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:08,280
Wait.

54
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:09,960
I promised her

55
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,879
I'd keep her safe.

56
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:12,680
Even if I have to level Zhao,

57
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,400
I will bring her back.

58
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:19,680
(Yue Qin, Shadow Bureau)

59
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,280
(Yue Qin, Shadow Bureau)
If the Shadow Bureau did this,

60
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:24,000
there's only one person who could

61
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,560
smuggle Yue Qin out of the city.

62
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,800
The Emperor.

63
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:34,960
The Zhao hostage prince
murdered our minister

64
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,240
and looted the treasury.

65
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,319
All he did

66
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,319
was trample the law

67
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:42,879
and dignity of Daliang underfoot!

68
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,759
Father,

69
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,479
Zhao has gone too far!

70
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,840
I'm willing to lead the army
and attack Zhao

71
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,520
to bring my wife home.

72
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:52,759
You?

73
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:55,080
You're a prince of Daliang.

74
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:57,599
Your consort colluded
with a Zhao hostage,

75
00:03:57,719 --> 00:03:59,000
killed my loyal minister,

76
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,159
and disgraced our empire.

77
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:01,840
Now she's fled,

78
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:03,560
and you knew nothing at all.

79
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,879
Aren't you ashamed to lead an army?

80
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,039
From today onward,

81
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:10,759
Murong Jinghe is stripped
of all military power

82
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,120
and confined to the palace.

83
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,800
Without my decree,

84
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,400
you shall not step outside!

85
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,800
Thank you, Father.

86
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,519
I will remain in confinement
and reflect.

87
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,399
Father,

88
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:34,560
the Zhao hostage stole
from the treasury and fled.

89
00:04:34,759 --> 00:04:35,879
I ask for your permission

90
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,279
to lead our forces against Zhao

91
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,920
and restore Daliang's honor.

92
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,720
Good.

93
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,120
Murong Xuanlie,

94
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,839
I entrust you

95
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,879
with Daliang's military power for now.

96
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,639
Don't let me down.

97
00:04:49,439 --> 00:04:50,839
I won't fail you, Father.

98
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:10,199
Jinghe, Father is right.

99
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,079
You should reflect on this well.

100
00:05:12,759 --> 00:05:15,240
Your merit and your consort,

101
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:17,759
I'll keep them both for you.

102
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:28,260
(State of Zhao)

103
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:35,839
(Where am I?)

104
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,240
Mei Lin, you're awake.

105
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,279
We're in Zhao now.

106
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,319
From now on,

107
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:44,319
this is our home.

108
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:45,759
I can protect you.

109
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:49,040
Yue Qin, you kidnapped me here.

110
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:51,560
Daliang's army will soon crush Zhao.

111
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,720
The people here will suffer.

112
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,639
The people?

113
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:59,000
What do they have to do with me?

114
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:00,680
Or are you

115
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:06,519
still hoping Murong Jinghe
will save you?

116
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:09,360
Do you think
he'd defy the Emperor's order

117
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,680
for your sake?

118
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:35,839
Don't worry, Your Highness.

119
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:35,920
Don't worry, Your Highness.

120
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,040
I'll hold the rear.

121
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,040
Let's go.

